cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves training neural networks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves developing unsupervised methods for discovering important neurons. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural networks, and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves analyzing representations learned by neural networks.
